      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2020 sedan in fair condition. The exterior has several small dents and noticeable scratches on multiple body panels. The interior shows moderate wear, including some stains on the upholstery and fading on the dashboard. All mechanical systems are functional but show signs of regular use.",
      "price": 21000.0,
