    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits moderate wear and some staining. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need a suspension tune-up and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind doing a bit of cosmetic or minor mechanical work.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
